1
00:00:07,458 --> 00:00:09,750
Katara: WATER...

2
00:00:09,792 --> 00:00:11,792
EARTH...

3
00:00:11,834 --> 00:00:13,917
FIRE...

4
00:00:13,959 --> 00:00:16,333
AIR.

5
00:00:16,375 --> 00:00:17,542
LONG AGO...

6
00:00:17,583 --> 00:00:19,959
THE FOUR NATIONS LIVED
TOGETHER IN HARMONY.

7
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,291
THEN EVERYTHING CHANGED
WHEN THE FIRE NATION ATTACKED.

8
00:00:24,333 --> 00:00:28,875
ONLY THE AVATAR,
MASTER OF ALL FOUR ELEMENTS
COULD STOP THEM.

9
00:00:28,917 --> 00:00:30,667
BUT WHEN THE WORLD
NEEDED HIM MOST

10
00:00:30,709 --> 00:00:31,917
HE VANISHED.

11
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:36,125
100 YEARS PASSED AND MY BROTHER
AND I DISCOVERED THE NEW AVATAR

12
00:00:36,166 --> 00:00:38,041
AN AIRBENDER NAMED AANG.

13
00:00:38,083 --> 00:00:40,333
AND ALTHOUGH HIS AIRBENDING
SKILLS WERE GREAT

14
00:00:40,375 --> 00:00:43,125
HE HAS A LOT TO LEARN BEFORE
HE'S READY TO SAVE ANYONE.

15
00:00:43,917 --> 00:00:47,041
BUT I BELIEVE AANG
CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

16
00:00:47,083 --> 00:00:52,041
♪

17
00:00:55,083 --> 00:00:56,542
I'M LOSING THIS WAR.

18
00:00:56,583 --> 00:00:59,208
I'M LETTING
THE WHOLE WORLD DOWN.

19
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:02,542
- I SHOULD HAVE SEEN
THIS WAR COMING,
AND PREVENTED IT.

20
00:01:03,083 --> 00:01:06,083
FOR SO LONG, I THOUGHT
THAT IF MY DAD ACCEPTED ME,
I'D BE HAPPY.

21
00:01:06,125 --> 00:01:07,250
I'M BACK HOME NOW.

22
00:01:07,291 --> 00:01:08,375
MY DAD TALKS TO ME.

23
00:01:08,417 --> 00:01:10,125
EVERYTHING SHOULD
BE PERFECT, RIGHT?

24
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:12,583
I SHOULD BE HAPPY NOW,
BUT I'M NOT.

25
00:01:12,625 --> 00:01:14,500
PLEASE, UNCLE, I'M SO CONFUSED.

26
00:01:14,542 --> 00:01:15,875
I NEED YOUR HELP.

27
00:01:16,709 --> 00:01:17,959
FORGET IT.

28
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,166
I'LL SOLVE THIS MYSELF.

29
00:01:19,208 --> 00:01:21,208
WASTE AWAY IN HERE
FOR ALL I CARE.

30
00:01:29,208 --> 00:01:33,959
- AANG, IT'S TIME YOU LEARNED
MY HISTORY WITH FIRE LORD SOZIN.

31
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:39,667
YOU NEED TO UNDERSTAND
HOW THE WAR BEGAN IF YOU WANT
TO KNOW HOW TO END IT.

32
00:01:40,542 --> 00:01:45,125
MEET MY ON MY HOME ISLAND ON
THE DAY OF THE SUMMER SOLSTICE.

33
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:49,041
OK, ROKU.

34
00:01:51,625 --> 00:01:54,417
[FOOTSTEPS]

35
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:05,917
YOU NEED TO KNOW THE STORY OF
YOUR GREAT-GRANDFATHER'S DEMISE.

36
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:08,208
IT WILL REVEAL YOUR OWN DESTINY.

37
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:21,709
[GROWLING]

38
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,750
Aang: THERE IT IS.

39
00:02:22,792 --> 00:02:27,500
THAT'S ROKU'S HOME.

40
00:02:27,542 --> 00:02:31,458
Katara: BUT THERE'S
NOTHING HERE.

41
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,792
YES, THERE IS.

42
00:02:32,834 --> 00:02:34,333
AN ENTIRE VILLAGE.

43
00:02:34,375 --> 00:02:36,041
HUNDREDS OF HOUSES.

44
00:02:36,083 --> 00:02:43,208
ALL COMPLETELY BURIED IN ASH.

45
00:02:43,250 --> 00:02:46,709
Azula: IT'S NEVER TOO EARLY
FOR A SITTING WITH
THE COURT PAINTER, ZUKO.

46
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:50,250
MAKE SURE HE GETS
YOUR GOOD SIDE.

47
00:02:50,291 --> 00:02:51,250
WAIT.

48
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,250
I NEED TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

49
00:02:53,291 --> 00:02:55,834
WHAT DO YOU REMEMBER ABOUT
OUR GREAT-GRANDFATHER'S HISTORY?

50
00:02:55,875 --> 00:02:56,875
AH, ZUKO.

51
00:02:56,917 --> 00:02:59,125
IT'S SO STRANGE
HOW YOUR MIND WORKS.

52
00:02:59,583 --> 00:03:02,250
FIRE LORD SOZIN BEGAN
THE WAR, OF COURSE.

53
00:03:02,291 --> 00:03:04,917
HE SPENT HIS EARLY YEARS
SECRETLY PREPARING FOR IT

54
00:03:04,959 --> 00:03:06,875
BUT HE WAS AS PATIENT
AS HE WAS CLEVER.

55
00:03:06,917 --> 00:03:11,000
HE FAMOUSLY WAITED
FOR THE COMET,
LATER RENAMED SOZIN'S COMET

56
00:03:11,041 --> 00:03:14,709
AND USED ITS POWER TO LAUNCH
HIS FULL-SCALE INVASION
OF THE WORLD.

57
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:18,250
IN THE END, HE DIED
A VERY OLD AND SUCCESSFUL MAN.

58
00:03:18,291 --> 00:03:19,667
BUT HOW DID HE DIE?

59
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,625
DIDN'T YOU PAY ANY ATTENTION
IN SCHOOL, ZUKO?

60
00:03:22,667 --> 00:03:24,750
HE DIED PEACEFULLY,
IN HIS SLEEP.

61
00:03:24,792 --> 00:03:26,083
HE WAS ANCIENT.

62
00:03:55,583 --> 00:03:57,041
WHAT DOES IT MEAN?

63
00:04:01,375 --> 00:04:02,166
[GASPING]

64
00:04:04,458 --> 00:04:09,709
THE FIRE SAGES KEEP
THE SECRET HISTORY IN
THE DRAGON BONE CATACOMBS.

65
00:05:05,458 --> 00:05:09,208
THE FINAL TESTAMENT
OF FIRE LORD SOZIN.

66
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:10,959
Roku: COME, AANG.

67
00:05:12,041 --> 00:05:13,375
Aang: WHERE ARE WE GOING?

68
00:05:13,417 --> 00:05:15,125
TO VISIT MY PAST.

69
00:05:15,625 --> 00:05:17,625
OUR SHARED PAST.

70
00:05:19,709 --> 00:05:23,625
Sozin: AS I FEEL
MY OWN LIFE DIMMING,
I CAN'T HELP BUT THINK

71
00:05:23,667 --> 00:05:27,542
OF A TIME WHEN EVERYTHING
WAS SO MUCH BRIGHTER.

72
00:05:28,583 --> 00:05:30,166
I REMEMBER MY FRIEND.

73
00:05:40,834 --> 00:05:43,417
[STAMMERING]

74
00:05:43,458 --> 00:05:46,083
[GRUNTING]

75
00:05:46,125 --> 00:05:47,959
LOOKS LIKE I WIN AGAIN, ROKU.

76
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,458
ARE YOU KIDDING?

77
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,166
THE TREE ROOT DID ALL THE WORK.

78
00:05:53,375 --> 00:05:55,041
NICE ONE, SOZIN.

79
00:05:55,083 --> 00:05:57,250
YOU WERE FRIENDS
WITH FIRE LORD SOZIN?

80
00:05:57,750 --> 00:06:03,000
BACK THEN,
HE WAS JUST PRINCE SOZIN,
AND HE WAS MY BEST FRIEND.

81
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:06,959
[SIGHING]

82
00:06:07,208 --> 00:06:08,709
SAY SOMETHING TO HER.

83
00:06:09,917 --> 00:06:14,083
UH... [SIGHING].

84
00:06:16,041 --> 00:06:18,875
- LOVE IS HARD WHEN YOU'RE
YOUNG.

85
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:20,583
YOU DON'T HAVE TO TELL ME.

86
00:06:20,625 --> 00:06:21,792
DON'T WORRY.

87
00:06:21,834 --> 00:06:23,375
IT GETS BETTER.

88
00:06:23,417 --> 00:06:24,792
NOW COME WITH ME.

89
00:06:25,458 --> 00:06:27,291
WE HAVE A PARTY TO ATTEND.

90
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:30,417
Aang: WAIT, WHOSE PARTY IS IT?

91
00:06:30,834 --> 00:06:35,625
Roku: SOZIN AND I
SHARED MANY THINGS,
INCLUDING A BIRTHDAY.

92
00:06:36,458 --> 00:06:38,125
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

93
00:06:38,166 --> 00:06:40,166
[LAUGHING SOFTLY]

94
00:06:40,208 --> 00:06:41,667
[GASPING]

95
00:06:42,834 --> 00:06:44,792
[LAUGHING]

96
00:06:47,125 --> 00:06:48,834
Sozin: DID SOMETHING HAPPEN
TO MY FATHER?

97
00:06:48,875 --> 00:06:50,208
NO, PRINCE SOZIN.

98
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:52,250
WE ARE NOT HERE FOR YOU.

99
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:55,917
WE ARE HERE TO ANNOUNCE THE
IDENTITY OF THE NEXT AVATAR.

100
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,542
-[GASPS]

101
00:06:57,583 --> 00:07:00,166
IT IS OUR HONOR TO SERVE YOU.

102
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:02,875
AVATAR, ROKU.

103
00:07:02,917 --> 00:07:09,458
♪

104
00:07:13,125 --> 00:07:15,792
Sozin: SOON, THE DAY CAME
WHEN MY FRIEND ROKU

105
00:07:15,834 --> 00:07:20,500
HAD TO LEAVE THE FIRE NATION
AND FACE HIS DESTINY
AS THE AVATAR.

106
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:25,333
HE NEEDED TO TRAVEL THE WORLD
SO HE COULD MASTER
THE OTHER ELEMENTS.

107
00:07:26,667 --> 00:07:29,750
HEY, WHY AREN'T YOU PACKED YET,
ALL-POWERFUL AVATAR?

108
00:07:32,041 --> 00:07:35,500
COME ON, SHOW ME HOW IT'S DONE
USING ALL FOUR KINDS OF BENDING.

109
00:07:39,041 --> 00:07:42,208
I STARTED PACKING,
BUT THEN THE FIRE SAGES TOLD ME

110
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:44,834
I WON'T NEED ANY
WORLDLY POSSESSIONS ANYMORE.

111
00:07:45,291 --> 00:07:46,208
OH.

112
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,417
IT HAPPENED SO FAST.

113
00:07:48,834 --> 00:07:50,834
EVERYTHING'S GONNA
BE DIFFERENT NOW.

114
00:07:54,375 --> 00:07:55,583
HERE.

115
00:07:55,625 --> 00:07:57,792
I HOPE YOU'RE AT LEAST
ALLOWED TO HAVE THIS.

116
00:07:57,834 --> 00:08:00,083
Roku: BUT THIS IS
A ROYAL ARTIFACT.

117
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:02,542
IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE WORN
BY THE CROWN PRINCE.

118
00:08:02,583 --> 00:08:04,291
I WANT YOU TO HAVE IT.

119
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:26,417
[GROANING]

120
00:08:26,875 --> 00:08:29,333
DO THEY HAVE BATHROOMS
IN THE SPIRIT WORLD?

121
00:08:29,375 --> 00:08:31,667
AS A MATTER OF FACT,
THEY DO NOT.

122
00:08:34,542 --> 00:08:37,208
HEY, WE'RE ALMOST AT
THE SOUTHERN AIR TEMPLE.

123
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:40,792
THIS WAS THE FIRST STOP
ON MY AVATAR JOURNEY.

124
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:44,834
IT WAS THE PLACE WHERE I WAS
TRAINED TO MASTER AIRBENDING

125
00:08:44,875 --> 00:08:50,333
AND ALSO WHERE I MET
AN OLD FRIEND OF YOURS,
MONK GYATSO.

126
00:08:50,375 --> 00:08:51,875
Aang: NO WAY.

127
00:08:56,709 --> 00:08:59,250
HEY, GYATSO, YOU WANT TO SEE
A NEW GLIDER TRICK?

128
00:09:02,834 --> 00:09:05,125
[LAUGHING], CHECK THIS OUT.

129
00:09:06,875 --> 00:09:08,083
Aang: HE'S AIR-SURFING.

130
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:10,291
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I NEVER THOUGHT OF THAT.

131
00:09:10,834 --> 00:09:12,792
[SCREAMING]

132
00:09:16,041 --> 00:09:17,375
[GASPING]

133
00:09:17,417 --> 00:09:20,125
[SCREAMING]

134
00:09:20,166 --> 00:09:22,834
[CRASHING]

135
00:09:23,208 --> 00:09:25,000
Aang: THAT'S AMAZING.

136
00:09:25,041 --> 00:09:27,875
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU
WERE FRIENDS WITH MONK GYATSO
JUST LIKE I WAS.

137
00:09:27,917 --> 00:09:34,500
SOME FRIENDSHIPS ARE SO STRONG,
THEY CAN EVEN
TRANSCEND LIFETIMES.

138
00:09:37,083 --> 00:09:43,375
AFTER MY YEARS
MASTERING AIRBENDING, I TRAVELED
TO THE NORTHERN WATER TRIBE.

139
00:09:44,417 --> 00:09:47,750
WATERBENDING WAS
ESPECIALLY CHALLENGING FOR ME.

140
00:09:51,041 --> 00:09:54,375
BUT IN TIME,
I MASTERED IT AS WELL.

141
00:09:56,333 --> 00:09:58,041
[SCREAMING]

142
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,709
I MOVED ON TO THE EARTH KINGDOM.

143
00:10:14,959 --> 00:10:20,792
MY EARTHBENDING MASTER, SUD, WAS
UNCOMPROMISING,
STUBBORN, AND BLUNT

144
00:10:22,917 --> 00:10:25,625
AND A LIFELONG FRIEND.

145
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,250
[LAUGHING]

146
00:10:28,959 --> 00:10:30,709
[GASPING]

147
00:10:38,959 --> 00:10:45,333
Roku: IT WAS BITTER WORK,
BUT THE RESULTS WERE WORTH IT.

148
00:10:53,166 --> 00:10:57,083
Sozin: TWELVE LONG YEARS PASSED
BEFORE I SAW MY FRIEND AGAIN.

149
00:10:57,417 --> 00:11:04,667
WHEN ROKU RETURNED,
HE WAS A FULLY REALIZED AVATAR,
AND I HAD CHANGED AS WELL.

150
00:11:05,166 --> 00:11:08,792
SOZIN, OR SHOULD I SAY,
FIRE LORD.

151
00:11:08,834 --> 00:11:15,625
CUSTOMARILY, MY SUBJECTS
BOW BEFORE GREETING ME,
BUT YOU'RE THE EXCEPTION.

152
00:11:18,083 --> 00:11:21,917
Roku: AFTER ALL THESE YEARS,
HE WAS STILL MY BEST FRIEND

153
00:11:22,667 --> 00:11:26,709
AND A FEW MONTHS LATER,
HE WAS MY BEST MAN.

154
00:11:29,959 --> 00:11:33,291
Aang: ROKU, IT'S THAT GIRL
WHO DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
YOU WERE ALIVE.

155
00:11:33,333 --> 00:11:34,959
Roku: TA MIN.

156
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:36,583
I WAS PERSISTENT.

157
00:11:36,625 --> 00:11:40,875
WHEN LOVE IS REAL,
IT FINDS A WAY

158
00:11:41,291 --> 00:11:46,166
AND BEING THE AVATAR
DOESN'T HURT YOUR CHANCES
WITH THE LADIES, EITHER.

159
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:50,792
Sozin: ON WEDDING DAYS,
WE LOOK TO THE FUTURE
WITH OPTIMISM AND JOY.

160
00:11:50,834 --> 00:11:54,542
I HAD MY OWN VISION
FOR A BRIGHTER FUTURE.

161
00:11:56,250 --> 00:11:57,917
EXCUSE ME.

162
00:11:57,959 --> 00:11:59,458
MAY I BORROW HIM FOR A MOMENT?

163
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:02,500
IT'S NOT VERY TRADITIONAL,
BUT OK.

164
00:12:05,166 --> 00:12:06,625
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND?

165
00:12:06,667 --> 00:12:09,834
I'VE BEEN THINKING HARD ABOUT
THE STATE OF THE WORLD LATELY.

166
00:12:09,875 --> 00:12:11,375
SOZIN, IT'S MY WEDDING.

167
00:12:11,417 --> 00:12:12,291
HAVE A COOKIE.

168
00:12:12,333 --> 00:12:13,667
DANCE WITH SOMEONE.

169
00:12:13,709 --> 00:12:14,834
LIGHTEN UP.

170
00:12:14,875 --> 00:12:17,125
I KNOW, I KNOW,
BUT JUST HEAR ME OUT.

171
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:23,000
RIGHT FROM THE START,
I WAS DESTINED TO BE FIRE LORD

172
00:12:23,041 --> 00:12:27,041
AND ALTHOUGH WE DIDN'T
ALWAYS KNOW IT, YOU WERE
DESTINED TO BE THE AVATAR.

173
00:12:27,083 --> 00:12:31,000
IT'S AN AMAZING STROKE OF FATE
WE KNOW EACH OTHER
SO WELL, ISN'T IT?

174
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:34,500
TOGETHER, WE COULD DO ANYTHING.

175
00:12:34,542 --> 00:12:37,291
YEAH, WE COULD.

176
00:12:37,333 --> 00:12:41,417
OUR NATION IS ENJOYING
AN UNPRECEDENTED TIME
OF PEACE AND WEALTH.

177
00:12:41,458 --> 00:12:46,250
OUR PEOPLE ARE HAPPY, AND WE'RE
SO FORTUNATE IN SO MANY WAYS.

178
00:12:46,291 --> 00:12:48,500
WHERE ARE YOU GOING WITH THIS?

179
00:12:48,542 --> 00:12:50,291
I'VE BEEN THINKING.

180
00:12:50,333 --> 00:12:53,625
WE SHOULD SHARE THIS PROSPERITY
WITH THE REST OF THE WORLD.

181
00:12:53,667 --> 00:12:57,125
IN OUR HANDS IS THE MOST
SUCCESSFUL EMPIRE IN HISTORY.

182
00:12:57,166 --> 00:12:59,583
IT'S TIME WE EXPANDED IT.

183
00:12:59,625 --> 00:13:00,917
NO.

184
00:13:00,959 --> 00:13:03,458
THE FOUR NATIONS ARE MEANT
TO BE JUST THAT: FOUR.

185
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:07,250
ROKU, YOU HAVEN'T EVEN STOPPED
TO CONSIDER THE POSSIBILITIES.

186
00:13:07,291 --> 00:13:09,166
THERE ARE NO POSSIBILITIES.

187
00:13:09,208 --> 00:13:11,583
THIS IS THE LAST I WANT
TO HEAR ABOUT THIS.

188
00:13:13,291 --> 00:13:16,959
<i>THAT WAS MY FIRST REAL TEST AS</i>
<i>THE AVATAR.</i>

189
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:20,667
<i>UNFORTUNATELY, IT WAS MANY YEARS</i>
<i>BEFORE I LEARNED THAT SOZIN</i>

190
00:13:20,709 --> 00:13:25,000
<i>HAD GONE AHEAD WITH HIS PLAN,</i>
<i>DESPITE MY WARNING.</i>

191
00:13:39,291 --> 00:13:41,542
I'VE SEEN THE COLONY, SOZIN.

192
00:13:41,583 --> 00:13:44,500
HOW DARE YOU OCCUPY
EARTH KINGDOM TERRITORY?

193
00:13:44,542 --> 00:13:50,792
Sozin: HOW DARE YOU,
A CITIZEN OF THE FIRE NATION,
ADDRESS YOUR FIRE LORD THIS WAY?

194
00:13:51,208 --> 00:13:54,875
YOUR LOYALTY IS
TO OUR NATION FIRST.

195
00:13:54,917 --> 00:13:57,250
ANYTHING LESS
MAKES YOU A TRAITOR.

196
00:13:57,291 --> 00:13:58,750
DON'T DO THIS, SOZIN.

197
00:13:58,792 --> 00:14:00,834
DON'T CHALLENGE ME.

198
00:14:00,875 --> 00:14:02,959
IT WILL ONLY END BADLY.

199
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:05,834
IT'S OVER.

200
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:19,583
[SCREAMING]

201
00:14:20,625 --> 00:14:23,208
[GRUNTING] 

202
00:14:38,166 --> 00:14:40,291
I'M SPARING YOU, SOZIN.

203
00:14:40,333 --> 00:14:43,792
I'M LETTING YOU GO IN THE NAME
OF OUR PAST FRIENDSHIP

204
00:14:43,834 --> 00:14:51,667
BUT I WARN YOU, EVEN A SINGLE
STEP OUT OF LINE WILL RESULT
IN YOUR PERMANENT END.

205
00:15:03,375 --> 00:15:06,250
Roku: SOZIN AND I DIDN'T
SPEAK OR SEE EACH OTHER

206
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:08,917
FOR 25 YEARS AFTER OUR BATTLE.

207
00:15:09,583 --> 00:15:13,917
I SPENT MOST OF MY SPARE TIME
HERE AT MY HOME.

208
00:15:15,583 --> 00:15:18,083
[WHOOSHING NOISE]

209
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:30,875
[COUGHING]

210
00:15:32,792 --> 00:15:34,125
Roku: LET'S GO.

211
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:11,542
Sozin: ROKU'S ISLAND
WAS 100 MILES AWAY.

212
00:16:11,583 --> 00:16:14,500
BUT I COULD STILL
FEEL IT RUMBLING

213
00:16:14,542 --> 00:16:17,417
AND SEE THE BLACK PLUME
OF SMOKE.

214
00:16:17,458 --> 00:16:21,041
I HAD NEVER SEEN ANYTHING
LIKE THIS CATASTROPHE.

215
00:17:13,083 --> 00:17:15,000
Aang: THIS IS AMAZING, ROKU.

216
00:17:15,041 --> 00:17:18,000
YOU'RE BATTLING A VOLCANO,
AND YOU'RE WINNING.

217
00:17:18,041 --> 00:17:22,083
UNFORTUNATELY, MY SUCCESS
DIDN'T LAST, AANG.

218
00:17:22,125 --> 00:17:25,000
THERE WAS NO WAY
I COULD DO IT ALL.

219
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:50,417
Roku: BATTLING THE ELEMENTS
WAS HARD ENOUGH

220
00:17:50,458 --> 00:17:53,125
I HAD TO DO IT WHILE
I COULD BARELY BREATHE.

221
00:17:53,166 --> 00:17:57,208
THE POISONOUS, VOLCANIC GASSES
WERE OVERWHELMING.

222
00:17:57,250 --> 00:17:59,750
[THUNDER CRASHES]

223
00:18:01,208 --> 00:18:02,625
[HOWLS]

224
00:18:02,667 --> 00:18:04,583
IT'S ALL RIGHT, FANG.
[COUGHS]

225
00:18:04,625 --> 00:18:08,625
GET OUT OF HERE, I'M FINE.

226
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:32,875
Sozin: NEED A HAND, OLD
FRIEND?

227
00:18:32,917 --> 00:18:34,417
SOZIN?

228
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,166
THERE'S NOT A MOMENT TO WASTE.

229
00:19:00,208 --> 00:19:02,125
[THUNDER CRASHES]

230
00:19:02,583 --> 00:19:04,583
[GASPS]

231
00:19:11,875 --> 00:19:14,709
Roku: DON'T BREATHE
THE TOXIC GAS.

232
00:19:21,333 --> 00:19:24,125
[COUGHS]

233
00:19:24,166 --> 00:19:27,709
IT'S... TOO MUCH.

234
00:19:28,458 --> 00:19:31,166
[GASPS AND COUGHS]

235
00:19:31,208 --> 00:19:32,875
PLEASE...

236
00:19:35,208 --> 00:19:38,917
WITHOUT YOU, ALL MY PLANS
ARE SUDDENLY POSSIBLE.

237
00:19:38,959 --> 00:19:41,917
I HAVE A VISION
FOR THE FUTURE, ROKU.

238
00:19:47,709 --> 00:19:49,834
[COUGHING...]

239
00:20:01,875 --> 00:20:03,959
[SCREECHES]

240
00:20:11,917 --> 00:20:13,458
[BABY CRIES]

241
00:20:15,875 --> 00:20:19,834
Aang: WHO'S, WAIT,
THAT'S ME, ISN'T IT?

242
00:20:19,875 --> 00:20:22,458
Roku: MAKE SENSE OF
OUR PAST, AANG.

243
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:27,667
AND YOU WILL BRING PEACE
AND RESTORE BALANCE
IN THE WORLD.

244
00:20:27,709 --> 00:20:29,000
Aang: ROKU?

245
00:20:29,041 --> 00:20:30,291
ROKU...

246
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:36,166
Sozin: WITH ROKU GONE,
AND THE GREAT COMET RETURNING

247
00:20:36,208 --> 00:20:39,542
THE TIMING WAS PERFECT
TO CHANGE THE WORLD.

248
00:20:39,583 --> 00:20:43,375
I KNEW THE NEXT AVATAR
WOULD BE BORN AN AIR NOMAD

249
00:20:43,625 --> 00:20:46,583
SO I WIPED OUT THE AIR TEMPLES.

250
00:20:46,625 --> 00:20:49,875
BUT SOMEHOW,
THE NEW AVATAR ELUDED ME.

251
00:20:49,917 --> 00:20:55,250
I WASTED THE REMAINDER OF
MY LIFE SEARCHING IN VAIN.

252
00:20:55,291 --> 00:20:57,750
I KNOW HE'S HIDING
OUT THERE SOMEWHERE

253
00:20:57,792 --> 00:21:00,500
THE FIRE NATION'S
GREATEST THREAT.

254
00:21:00,542 --> 00:21:03,333
THE LAST AIRBENDER.

255
00:21:06,792 --> 00:21:10,125
THAT CAN'T BE IT,
WHERE'S THE REST OF IT?

256
00:21:18,834 --> 00:21:21,083
YOU SENT THIS, DIDN'T YOU?

257
00:21:21,125 --> 00:21:23,208
I FOUND THE SECRET HISTORY.

258
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:26,583
WHICH, BY THE WAY,
SHOULD BE RENAMED "THE HISTORY
MOST PEOPLE ALREADY KNOW."

259
00:21:26,625 --> 00:21:30,250
THE NOTE SAID THAT
I NEEDED TO KNOW ABOUT MY
GREAT-GRANDFATHER'S DEATH

260
00:21:30,291 --> 00:21:32,000
BUT HE WAS STILL ALIVE
IN THE END.

261
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:34,834
NO, HE WASN'T.

262
00:21:34,875 --> 00:21:36,542
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

263
00:21:36,583 --> 00:21:40,166
Iroh: YOU HAVE MORE THAN ONE
GREAT-GRANDFATHER, PRINCE ZUKO.

264
00:21:40,417 --> 00:21:43,250
SOZIN WAS YOUR
FATHER'S GRANDFATHER.

265
00:21:43,291 --> 00:21:47,458
YOUR<i> MOTHER'S</i> GRANDFATHER
WAS AVATAR ROKU.

266
00:21:48,959 --> 00:21:50,792
WHY ARE YOU TELLING ME THIS?

267
00:21:50,834 --> 00:21:55,625
BECAUSE UNDERSTANDING
THE STRUGGLE BETWEEN
YOUR TWO GREAT-GRANDFATHERS

268
00:21:55,667 --> 00:22:00,333
CAN HELP YOU BETTER UNDERSTAND
THE BATTLE WITHIN YOURSELF.

269
00:22:02,166 --> 00:22:06,000
EVIL AND GOOD ARE ALWAYS
AT WAR INSIDE YOU, ZUKO

270
00:22:06,041 --> 00:22:08,792
IT IS YOUR NATURE, YOUR LEGACY.

271
00:22:08,834 --> 00:22:11,875
BUT THERE IS A BRIGHT SIDE.

272
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:17,208
WHAT HAPPENED GENERATIONS AGO
CAN BE RESOLVED NOW.

273
00:22:17,250 --> 00:22:19,000
BY YOU.

274
00:22:19,041 --> 00:22:24,625
BECAUSE OF YOUR LEGACY,
YOU ALONE CAN CLEANSE THE SINS
OF OUR FAMILY

275
00:22:24,667 --> 00:22:26,542
AND THE FIRE NATION.

276
00:22:26,583 --> 00:22:29,667
BORN IN YOU,
ALONG WITH ALL THIS STRIFE

277
00:22:29,709 --> 00:22:34,709
IS THE POWER TO RESTORE BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

278
00:22:39,083 --> 00:22:42,375
THIS IS A ROYAL ARTIFACT.

279
00:22:42,417 --> 00:22:47,041
IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE WORN
BY THE CROWN PRINCE.

280
00:22:55,917 --> 00:22:59,208
Katara: YOU MEAN,
AFTER ALL ROKU AND SOZIN
WENT THROUGH TOGETHER

281
00:22:59,250 --> 00:23:03,166
EVEN AFTER ROKU
SHOWED HIM MERCY,
SOZIN BETRAYED HIM LIKE THAT?

282
00:23:03,208 --> 00:23:05,917
IT'S LIKE THESE PEOPLE
ARE BORN BAD.

283
00:23:05,959 --> 00:23:07,583
Aang: NO, THAT'S WRONG.

284
00:23:07,625 --> 00:23:10,625
I DON'T THINK THAT WAS THE POINT
OF WHAT ROKU SHOWED ME AT ALL.

285
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,375
THEN WHAT WAS THE POINT?

286
00:23:12,417 --> 00:23:15,625
ROKU WAS JUST AS MUCH
FIRE NATION AS SOZIN WAS, RIGHT?

287
00:23:15,667 --> 00:23:20,000
IF ANYTHING, THEIR STORY PROVES
ANYONE'S CAPABLE OF
GREAT GOOD AND GREAT EVIL.

288
00:23:20,041 --> 00:23:23,000
EVERYONE, EVEN THE FIRE LORD
AND THE FIRE NATION

289
00:23:23,041 --> 00:23:25,375
HAVE TO BE TREATED LIKE
THEY'RE WORTH GIVING A CHANCE.

290
00:23:25,417 --> 00:23:28,458
AND I ALSO THINK IT WAS
ABOUT FRIENDSHIPS.

291
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:32,792
DO YOU REALLY THINK FRIENDSHIPS
CAN LAST MORE THAN ONE LIFETIME?

292
00:23:34,125 --> 00:23:35,750
I DON'T SEE WHY NOT.

293
00:23:35,792 --> 00:23:38,792
Sokka: WELL, SCIENTIFICALLY
SPEAKING, THERE'S NO WAY
TO PROVE THAT-

294
00:23:38,834 --> 00:23:40,625
Katana: OH SOKKA, JUST HOLD
HANDS.

295
00:23:43,583 --> 00:23:49,333
♪

296
00:23:52,250 --> 00:23:55,250
[MEN VOCALIZING RHYTHMICALLY...]
